[{"Code":"en","Title":"Alipay","Slug":"alipay","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mi4bvg2u-9wa6zl-253\"><img data-block-id=\"mi8han1c-gentr9-002\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/433660082_801170242047085_8779791849550767212_n.jpg\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"Alipay logo featuring a stylized '支' symbol and the word 'Alipay'.\" width=\"201\" height=\"58\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:201px;height:58px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mi4bvg2u-9wa6zl-253\">Alipay  refers to the e-wallet and digital payment service by the Chinese company Ant Group that operates in Malaysia, allowing users to make cashless payments online and in stores<span type=\"spanMark\" style=\"color:rgb(10, 10, 10);background:rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;font-weight:400;text-transform:none;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;float:none;display:inline !important;\">. It is accepted by many merchants, particularly popular with tourists, and partners with Malaysian banks to facilitate transactions. Users can pay for goods and services by scanning QR codes or using their linked cards.</span><span class=\"uJ19be notranslate\" type=\"spanMark\" style=\"color:rgb(10, 10, 10);background:rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;font-weight:400;text-transform:none;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\"><span class=\"vKEkVd\" type=\"spanNode\" style=\"position:relative;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p data-block-id=\"mi4bveun-r70gac-252\"><span type=\"spanMark\" style=\"color:rgb(214, 220, 228);\">_________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________</span></p><h2 data-block-id=\"mi4bxxy8-j4z6nj-379\">Features</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"878\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:878px;width:878px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:300px;\"><col style=\"width:578px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxy9-s74xb2-380\"><strong>Channel Code</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxya-abovpw-381\"><span type=\"spanMark\" style=\"color:rgb(17, 24, 39);background:rgb(243, 244, 246);font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.02em;display:inline-block;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:6px;\">ALIPAY</span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxya-4vp6co-382\"><strong>Display Name</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyb-mwngrv-383\">Alipay</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyb-yordub-384\"><strong>Currency</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyc-mb6vel-385\">MYR</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyc-9bk34l-386\"><strong>Country</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyc