"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyh-wdjk43-401\">✓</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyi-kx5zgl-402\"><strong>Auth &amp; Capture</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyi-dpjc15-403\">-</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyi-galvkd-404\"><strong>Partial Capture</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyj-am40ue-405\">-</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyj-q0cqmn-406\"><strong>Multiple Partial Capture</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyk-qcm8h7-407\">-</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyk-kvlo5m-408\"><strong>Desktop Support</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyk-tm9v01-409\">WEB URL</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyl-u6s8wa-410\"><strong>Mobile Support</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyl-kekigh-411\">MOBILE WEB URL</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyl-ym6jx2-412\"><strong>Custom Payment Code</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxym-alqk14-413\">-</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxym-yd9feb-414\"><strong>Display Merchant Name</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxym-98lqkp-415\">MERCHANT</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyn-27jg7m-416\"><strong>Display User Name</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyn-bdhes0-417\">-</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyn-r3h27a-418\"><strong>Set Expiry</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyo-04jgcl-419\">-</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyo-s3deyh-420\"><strong>Payment Request Expiry (hours)</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyp-nhnzt5-421\">0.17</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyp-bzmk5u-422\"><strong>Payment Token Validity (years)</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyp-fxwut1-423\">-</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyq-ic3c07-424\"><strong>Payment Processing Time (hours)</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyq-1mpkm2-425\">INSTANT</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyq-chueba-426\"><strong>Settlement Time</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyr-8flinq-427\">T+2 CALENDAR DAYS*</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyr-7ojehp-428\"><strong>Installments</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyr-p53fr4-429\">-</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxys-i5peqt-430\"><strong>Refund</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxys-wpfhus-431\">✓</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxys-txtb0p-432\"><strong>Partial Refund</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyt-fs6uss-433\">✓</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyt-3bz947-434\"><strong>Multiple Partial Refund</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyt-8j48sl-435\">✓</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyu-pcuh23-436\"><strong>Refund Validity (days)</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyu-7luxuv-437\">365</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyv-gq2v9n-438\"><strong>Payment Link</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyv-5vvi6p-439\">✓</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyv-a3g2og-440\"><strong>Fund Flow</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p data-block-id=\"mi4bxxyw-6hecm5-441\">AGGREGATOR</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mmk0chrk-10vipu-559\">Payment flow</h2><p data-block-id=\"mmk0chrk-m89fgq-560\">For <strong>desktop users</strong>, the payment process includes displaying the list of available payment method in the available merchant and country. End user will be able to scan (in desktop), jump app (in mobile) or log in to particular payment method to proceed the payment.</p><div data-role=\"tabs-container\" class=\"tabs\"><div data-role=\"tab-header-container\" class=\"tab-header\"><div data-tab-id=\"f1fa8805-9ab0-43ec-989b-ea1a3f929ba5\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"tab active\" data-role=\"tab\" style=\"background-color:rgb(244, 244, 245);border-color:rgb(209, 209, 214);\"><label title=\"Desktop View\">Desktop View</label></div><div data-tab-id=\"99d0956d-99d2-449f-ae24-d73233775bd7\" contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"tab\" data-role=\"tab\" style=\"background-color:rgb(244, 244, 245);border-color:rgb(209, 209, 214);\"><label title=\"Mobile View\">Mobile View</label></div></div><div data-role=\"tab-content-container\" class=\"tab-content\" style=\"background-color:rgb(244, 244, 245);border-color:rgb(209, 209, 214);\"><div data-content-id=\"f1fa8805-9ab0-43ec-989b-ea1a3f929ba5\" class=\"content active\" data-role=\"content\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk0m7j7-sl6fqq-580\"><img data-block-id=\"mmk0mlmn-siy2m6-582\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(193).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"556\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" _ngcontent-ng-c1691667138=\"\" data-cy=\"imageNodeView\" data-align=\"left\" data-display=\"flex\" style=\"width:556px;\"></p></div><div data-content-id=\"99d0956d-99d2-449f-ae24-d73233775bd7\" class=\"content\" data-role=\"content\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk0ovr1-826h0o-585\"><img data-block-id=\"mmk0s7z9-8m7zcn-002\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(196).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"290\" height=\"462\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:290px;height:462px;\"></p></div></div></div><p data-block-id=\"mmk0chrk-tutljw-561\">The payment processing will follow the process based on the selected payment method.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmk0pz27-h5tl90-586\"><video src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/alipay.mp4\" mediatype=\"video\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" data-type=\"media-content\" controls=\"true\" style=\"display:flex;margin-right:auto;width:640px;height:360px;\">null</video></p><p></p>","SeoTitle":"Alipay","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"AliPay","Slug":"alipay","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"AliPay","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"AliPay","Slug":"alipay","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"AliPay","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"AliPay","Slug":"alipay","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"AliPay","Description":null}]